videos.description: Georgia's Nicolas Claxton steals the ball and finishes the fast break with a Eurostep leading to a dunk.
videos.headline: Claxton Eurosteps his way to a dunk off the steal

videos.description: Kentucky's Ashton Hagans sees an opening for an easy steal a capitalizes on it with the transition layup.
videos.headline: Hagans sneaks behind for a steal for transition bucket

videos.description: Kentucky's EJ Montgomery catches the alley-oop from Ashton Hagans for a monster dunk.
videos.headline: Hagans lobs it up for a Montgomery slam
